  "remarks": "National identification no.: Saudi Arabian national identity card number 1089516791. Operational commander of Al-Qaida in the Arabian Peninsula (AQAP) (QE.A.129.10.). Has been involved in raising funds and stockpiling arms for AQAP operations and activities in Yemen. Known associate of Qasim Yahya Mahdi al-Rimi (QI.A.282.10.) and Fahd Mohammed Ahmed al-Quso (QI.A.288.10.). INTERPOL Orange Notice (file number 2009/52/OS/CCC, #14). INTERPOL Red Notice (Control Number A-596/3-2009, File Number 2009/3731). Father’s name is Ahmed Othman Al Omirah. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 16 June 2011 (amended on 24 Nov. 2020)",
